gobblin.source.extractor

Interface Extractor<S,D>

  • Type Parameters:
    S - output schema type
    D - output record type
    All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Closeable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    StreamingExtractor<S,D>

    public interface Extractor<S,D>
extends Closeable
    An interface for classes that are responsible for extracting data from a data source.

    All source specific logic for a data source should be encapsulated in an implementation of this interface and Source.
